{"tid":968550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國外交部陸慷：美方的赴華旅行提示經不起推敲","createTime":"2019-01-04T10:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T10:55:09.000Z","uid":147314,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"104ae4677be3be75d03e7861fe2234896df4a34f","tid":968550,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T10:23:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">外交部指美方的赴華旅行提示經不起推敲</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">2019-01-04 HKT 16:49</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1436478_1_L_20190104164944.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1436478_1_L_20190104164944.jpg&h=8009167b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">陸慷批評美方近年來以各種理由和藉口，對中國公民入境美國設置障礙及無端進行檢查。（港台圖片）</span><br />\n<br />\n美國國務院在網站提醒國民前往中國旅行時，要慎防中國可能「任意執法」。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人陸慷回應說，中方歡迎包括美國公民在內的外國公民來華，並依法保障其在華的安全和合法權益，而針對極少數涉嫌在華違法犯罪的外國公民，中國辦案機關始終堅持依法公正處理，認為美方發布的赴華旅行提示經不起推敲，又批評美方近年來以各種理由和藉口，對中國公民入境美國設置障礙及無端進行檢查，要求美方重視和糾正。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1436478-20190104.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1436478-20190104.htm&d=xaOXq7AbvXm4czYf0%2FFKqm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=da2cbf94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1436478-20190104.htm&h=aed8b57a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1436478-20190104.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6be3f7cb99647d274cb46d8f7611a3d2950f6d4a","tid":968550,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T10:55:09.000Z","msg":"鄰國係依法，不過佢自己就係法律，個龍門任佢搬啫"}]}